Use the following commands to clone/install everything need for a new wordpress website using AFBFramework.

##STEPS FOR NEW SITE SETUP##
----------------------------

1. git clone https://github.com/stevecordle/AFBDefault.git .
2. git submodule init
3. git submodule update
4. cd wordpress && git checkout 4.2.1 (or current Version)
5. composer selfupdate
6. composer update
7. npm install
8. 

----------------------------
Copy paste the below to go thru all of the steps with one lin

    git clone https://github.com/stevecordle/AFBDefault.git . && git submodule init && git submodule update && cd wordpress && git checkout 4.2.1 && cd .. && composer selfupdate && composer update && npm install
